Write CSV to database

Source: R/write_csv_to_db.R
write_csv_to_db.Rd

Write CSV to database

Usage

write_csv_to_db(path, file_name = "results.db")

Arguments

path

filepath; where input files are located relative to `config`.

file_name

The name of the database file to write to. Default is "results.db".

Value

file path to the database.
